{"tid":1743634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊推《榮光》上903我最喜愛歌曲！","createTime":"2019-11-21T09:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:41:43.000Z","uid":45167,"like":186,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd786a397e42fa5330a6927dde1e71c01b2c8a4","tid":1743634,"uid":45167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"何韻詩話：<br />\n關於推《榮光》903我最喜愛歌曲<br />\n<br />\n歌曲入圍投票條件：<br />\n<br />\n1）必須上榜起碼一週<br />\n2）如要上到榜20位內，首歌起碼要一週（由星期三到下一個星期二）內播到10次<br />\n3）deadline：7/12/2019，第49週<br />\n<br />\n建議做法：<br />\n<br />\n上榜必須DJ們幫手，其實過去都有DJ朋友播，但比較散，加埋一週內次數唔夠。因為時日無多，如果想一致推上榜，建議做法可以係：盡量諗辦法爭取DJ支持，夾定下週（27/11-4/12）推，每個節目時段播一次。<br />\n<br />\n為加強成效，要大家幫手做文宣/圖。大家亦可以用ig或fb PM或Tag各節目DJ，請佢地幫忙喺節目播，三四日內夠10次就應該可以上榜，上到榜就可以納入「我最喜愛歌曲」候選歌曲投票。<br />\n搵人推去連登，我啲廢中無account<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔理佢有無進化<br />\n唔理佢係咪左膠<br />\n重點係要推《榮光》上903！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"48e88812a9aba8d47c624e509ed88c8d898e1965","tid":1743634,"uid":45167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"十連推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6a90a7bd87cdcbe51bf19b6edfbd05faf346dc","tid":1743634,"uid":45167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"十連推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fbf215493e798b6778c4b6ca6f06fe187a28fc","tid":1743634,"uid":245988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bd788787bee68b3eb760d178f30eced672886b6","tid":1743634,"uid":245988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"Tui1"},{"pid":"d41c487c81c9c93a818a90804fa48e2fa7a166a6","tid":1743634,"uid":245988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"Tui2"},{"pid":"a070557d19c72166b95d09f171cb2625ae2bdb9a","ti